PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump said the US
OL,8,Fdestroyed military sites on an island
OL,9,Fvital to Iran's oil network and warned
OL,10,Fthat its oil infrastructure could be
OL,11,Fnext if Iran continues to interfere
OL,12,Fwith the passage of ships through the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,15,FTrump said US forces on Friday
OL,16,F"obliterated" targets on Iran's Kharg
OL,17,FIsland, which is home to the primary
OL,18,Fterminal that handles the country's
OL,19,Foil exports.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
