FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe speaker of the Iranian parliament
OL,8,Fhad warned that such strikes would
OL,9,Fprovoke a new level of retaliation.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, an American official said
OL,12,F2,500 more Marines and an amphibious
OL,13,Fassault ship are being sent to the
OL,14,FMiddle East nearly two weeks into the
OL,15,Fwar with the Islamic Republic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
