CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FIran has continued to launch
OL,8,Fwidespread missile and drone attacks
OL,9,Fon Israel and neighbouring Gulf
OL,10,Fstates, and effectively closed the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz, through which a
OL,12,Ffifth of the world's traded oil
OL,13,Fpasses, even as US and Israeli
OL,14,Fwarplanes pummel military and other
OL,15,Ftargets across Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe humanitarian crisis in Lebanon
OL,8,Fdeepened, with nearly 800 people
OL,9,Fkilled and 850,000 displaced as Israel
OL,10,Flaunched waves of strikes against Iran-
OL,11,Fbacked Hezbollah militants and warned
OL,12,Fthere would be no let-up.
OL,14,FElements from the 31st Marine
OL,15,FExpeditionary Unit and the amphibious
OL,16,Fassault ship USS Tripoli have been
OL,17,Fordered to the Middle East, according
OL,18,Fto the US official, who spoke to The
OL,19,FAssociated Press on condition of
OL,20,Fanonymity to discuss sensitive
OL,21,Fmilitary plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FMarine Expeditionary Units are able to
OL,8,Fconduct amphibious landings, but they
OL,9,Falso specialise in bolstering security
OL,10,Fat embassies, evacuating civilians,
OL,11,Fand providing disaster relief. The
OL,12,Fdeployment does not necessarily
OL,13,Findicate that a ground operation is
OL,14,Fimminent or will take place.
OL,16,FThe Wall Street Journal first reported
OL,17,Fthe new Marine deployment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe 31st Marine Expeditionary Unit, as
OL,8,Fwell as the Tripoli and other
OL,9,Famphibious assault ships carrying the
OL,10,FMarines, are based in Japan and have
OL,11,Fbeen in the Pacific Ocean for several
OL,12,Fdays, according to images released by
OL,13,Fthe military.
OL,15,FThe Tripoli was spotted by commercial
OL,16,Fsatellites sailing alone near Taiwan,
OL,17,Fputting it more than a week away from
OL,18,Fthe waters off Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FEarlier in the week, the Navy had 12
OL,8,Fships, including the aircraft carrier
OL,9,FUSS Abraham Lincoln and eight
OL,10,Fdestroyers, operating in the Arabian
OL,11,FSea. Should the Tripoli join this
OL,12,Fflotilla, it would be the second-
OL,13,Flargest ship behind the Lincoln in the
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,16,FWhile the total number of US service
OL,17,Fmembers on the ground in the Middle
OL,18,FEast is not clear, Al-Udeid Air Base
OL,19,Falone, one of the largest in the
OL,20,Fregion, typically houses some 8,000 US
OL,21,Ftroops in Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe US strikes on Iran's Kharg Island
OL,8,Fin the Persian Gulf targeted military
OL,9,Fsites but left its oil infrastructure
OL,10,Falone for now, Trump said in a social
OL,11,Fmedia post.
OL,13,FBut he warned that if Iran or anyone
OL,14,Felse interferes with the passage of
OL,15,Fships through the Strait of Hormuz, he
OL,16,Fwill reconsider his decision not to
OL,17,F"wipe out the Oil Infrastructure."
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
