PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FIranian parliament Speaker Mohammad
OL,8,FBagher Qalibaf warned on Thursday in a
OL,9,Fsocial media post that attacks on the
OL,10,Fislands on Iran's southern maritime
OL,11,Ffrontier would cause Iran to "abandon
OL,12,Fall restraint," underscoring how
OL,13,Fcentral they are to the country's
OL,14,Feconomy and security.
OL,16,FOn Saturday, Iran's joint military
OL,17,Fcommand reiterated its threat that it
OL,18,Fwill attack the US-linked oil and
OL,19,Fenergy facilities in the region if the
OL,20,FIslamic Republic's oil infrastructure
OL,21,Fis hit.
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
