PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FEbrahim Zolfaghari, spokesperson for
OL,8,Fthe Khatam al-Anbiya Central
OL,9,FHeadquarters, warned they will target
OL,10,F"all oil, economic, and energy
OL,11,Finfrastructures belonging to oil
OL,12,Fcompanies across the region that have
OL,13,FAmerican shares or cooperate with
OL,14,FAmerica."
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
