PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe joint military command also
OL,8,Fthreatened to attack cities in the
OL,9,FUnited Arab Emirates, saying the U.S.
OL,10,Fused "ports, docks and hideouts"
OL,11,Fwithin UAE cities to launch strikes on
OL,12,Fthe islands, without providing
OL,13,Fevidence. It called on people to
OL,14,Fevacuate those areas where it said
OL,15,FU.S. forces were sheltering
OL,17,FIran's semiofficial Fars news agency
OL,18,Fon Saturday said the US strikes caused
OL,19,Fno damage to oil infrastructure on the
OL,20,Fisland.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
