PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FIt reported at least 15 explosions
OL,8,Ffollowed the strikes, which it said
OL,9,Ftargeted an air defence facility, a
OL,10,Fnaval base, the airport control tower
OL,11,Fand an offshore oil company's
OL,12,Fhelicopter hangar.
OL,14,FA missile struck a helipad inside the
OL,15,FUS Embassy compound in Baghdad, two
OL,16,FIraqi security officials said.
OL,18,FAssociated Press footage showed a
OL,19,Fcolumn of smoke rising Saturday
OL,20,Fmorning over the embassy compound.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FThe sprawling embassy complex, one of
OL,8,Fthe largest US diplomatic facilities
OL,9,Fin the world, has been repeatedly
OL,10,Ftargeted by rockets and drones fired
OL,11,Fby Iran-aligned militias.
OL,13,FThere was no immediate comment from
OL,14,Fthe US Embassy in Baghdad. On Friday,
OL,15,Fthe embassy renewed its Level 4
OL,16,Fsecurity alert for Iraq, warning that
OL,17,FIran and Iran-aligned militia groups
OL,18,Fhave previously carried out attacks
OL,19,Fagainst US citizens, interests and
OL,20,Finfrastructure, and "may continue to
OL,21,Ftarget them."
OL,26,@|D@UOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FIsrael earlier announced another wave
OL,8,Fof strikes in Iran targeting
OL,9,Finfrastructure, and said its air force
OL,10,Fhad hit more than 200 targets in the
OL,11,Flast 24 hours, including missile
OL,12,Flaunchers, defence systems and weapons
OL,13,Fproduction sites.
OL,15,FIn Washington, US Defence Secretary
OL,16,FPete Hegseth said that over 15,000
OL,17,Fenemy targets have been struck ` more
OL,18,Fthan 1,000 a day since the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
