SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773558304
OL,3,CUS bombs military sites on Iranian
OL,4,Cisland as Trump threatens oil
OL,5,Cinfrastructure
OL,7,FHe also sought to address concerns
OL,8,Fabout the bottling of the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz, telling reporters: "We have
OL,10,Fbeen dealing with it and don't need to
OL,11,Fworry about it."
